<br>
for the majority if level 35-45 players theres no incentive or interest in going out to engage in rvr. basically because its dominated by level 50 players.  players more then 5 levels below 50,are generally worthless,except in specific things like keep taking. <br>
<br>
theres no incentive to be on your own frontier,because your only reward is death,and wasting your time. this basically means most people in this level range,are of the mindset that they have to level via pve to be able to engage successfully in rvr combat. given that every level is essentially an eq hell level,people tend to burn out between 40-45 because it stops being fun and enjoyable and turns into a mindless experience grind. <br>
